550
00:31:55,705 --> 00:31:57,505
It said if she had bipolar disorder...

551
00:32:18,295 --> 00:32:19,855
What's the deal with Kim Ram Woo and Bang Ji Su?

552
00:32:20,095 --> 00:32:22,325
Did you see what happened? It was crazy.

553
00:32:31,905 --> 00:32:33,135
What happened?

554
00:32:34,075 --> 00:32:35,175
It's over.

555
00:32:35,605 --> 00:32:36,904
After he brought you into the infirmary,

556
00:32:36,905 --> 00:32:38,215
Ji Su asked him out right there.

557
00:32:41,885 --> 00:32:43,145
