624
00:36:04,515 --> 00:36:07,085
Get back at you? Why would I want to do that?

625
00:36:07,215 --> 00:36:09,884
Then why are you doing this to me?

626
00:36:09,885 --> 00:36:12,524
My gosh, come on. Stop talking to yourself.

627
00:36:12,525 --> 00:36:15,025
They think you're a weirdo and won't let you do it.

628
00:36:16,195 --> 00:36:17,525
Gosh, I hate it.

629
00:36:17,765 --> 00:36:20,165
You look so awful right now.

630
00:36:28,805 --> 00:36:29,845
Are you okay?

631
00:36:30,775 --> 00:36:32,745
There was also something...

632
00:36:33,315 --> 00:36:34,985
