647
00:37:10,515 --> 00:37:11,984
You're here because you wanted to do this.

648
00:37:11,985 --> 00:37:13,214
Hey, how can I possibly do this?

649
00:37:13,215 --> 00:37:14,284
You must be out of your mind.

650
00:37:14,285 --> 00:37:16,284
- Have you lost your mind? - All right.

651
00:37:16,285 --> 00:37:17,654
- Let's go. We can do this. - Wait.

652
00:37:17,655 --> 00:37:19,394
