653
00:37:19,395 --> 00:37:21,094
- Wait. No, sir. - Okay!

654
00:37:21,095 --> 00:37:22,194
- You... - It's okay.

655
00:37:22,195 --> 00:37:23,224
- Look over there. That looks fun! - Wait.

656
00:37:23,225 --> 00:37:24,264
He's...

657
00:37:24,265 --> 00:37:25,664
- That looks fun. - Have fun, Ram Woo.

658
00:37:25,665 --> 00:37:26,694
- You... - All right.

659
00:37:26,695 --> 00:37:28,364
- Good luck. - You got this. You'll be fine.

660
00:37:28,365 --> 00:37:29,365
- Please. - My gosh.

661
00:37:29,366 --> 00:37:31,004
- See you down there! - My gosh.

662
00:37:31,005 --> 00:37:32,274
- Don't cry. - But...

663
00:37:32,275 --> 00:37:33,374
It's okay.

664
00:37:33,375 --> 00:37:34,904
- It's not scary. - Is this safe?

665
00:37:34,905 --> 00:37:35,944
- Look over there. - All right.

666
00:37:35,945 --> 00:37:37,144
- Run! - Hold on!

667
00:37:37,145 --> 00:37:38,275
Wait!

668
00:37:38,845 --> 00:37:39,875
- You'll be fine. - Wait.

669
00:37:40,845 --> 00:37:42,985
- No! - It's okay!

670
00:37:43,415 --> 00:37:44,684
- It's okay! - It's okay!

671
00:37:44,685 --> 00:37:47,285
Have a blast!

672
00:37:50,385 --> 00:37:52,525
Are you sure this is safe? Wait.

673
00:37:53,495 --> 00:37:56,195
My gosh. Hold on!

674
00:38:10,675 --> 00:38:12,774
- That was fast. - Given our friendship,

675
00:38:12,775 --> 00:38:15,145
I did the platinum version for the letter.

676
00:38:16,145 --> 00:38:17,145
Thanks.

677
00:38:19,755 --> 00:38:20,755
"Ji Su?"

678
00:38:21,385 --> 00:38:22,685
Why did you write "Ji Su?"

679
00:38:23,655 --> 00:38:26,325
JS. It stands for Ji Su, your girlfriend.

680
00:38:27,055 --> 00:38:28,295
My girlfriend?

681
00:38:30,025 --> 00:38:31,065
No.

682
00:38:31,465 --> 00:38:32,935
JS stands for Jeong Suk.

683
00:38:33,165 --> 00:38:34,234
Jeong Suk?

684
00:38:34,235 --> 00:38:35,865
Who's Jeong Suk? Which class is she in?

685
00:38:36,405 --> 00:38:37,935
She's my mother.

686
00:38:39,575 --> 00:38:40,605
What?

687
00:38:41,375 --> 00:38:42,505
She's my mother.

688
00:38:43,375 --> 00:38:45,375
She thinks that's an old name and hates it when I call her that.

689
00:38:48,715 --> 00:38:51,854
So you wrote this love letter not for Ji Su,

690
00:38:51,855 --> 00:38:52,915
but for your mother?

691
00:38:53,115 --> 00:38:54,315
It's not a love letter.

692
00:38:54,685 --> 00:38:56,655
It's a letter for her birthday.

693
00:38:57,455 --> 00:39:00,525
Hey, that's why you thanked her for her hard work in the letter.

694
00:39:01,395 --> 00:39:03,625
- Yes. - I see.

695
00:39:03,865 --> 00:39:06,265
Anyway, I can just fix the name in the letter.

696
00:39:07,295 --> 00:39:08,734
So it was 45 dollars, right?

697
00:39:08,735 --> 00:39:11,264
Hey, no. You don't have to pay me. Come on, it's me.

698
00:39:11,265 --> 00:39:12,574
You keep it.

699
00:39:12,575 --> 00:39:14,235
- No, but still. I... - No, keep it.

700
00:39:15,105 --> 00:39:16,175
Keep it.

701
00:39:17,845 --> 00:39:18,875
Keep it.

702
00:39:20,075 --> 00:39:21,315
- Thanks. - Sure.

703
00:39:27,155 --> 00:39:28,285
Jung Hee Wan.

704
00:39:29,025 --> 00:39:30,155
Then...

705
00:39:31,085 --> 00:39:32,695
what about Ji Su? Didn't she ask you out?

706
00:39:33,825 --> 00:39:35,695
