708
00:39:38,095 --> 00:39:40,495
You said you were sorry? You turned her down?

709
00:39:41,065 --> 00:39:42,265
Why did you turn her down?

710
00:39:45,375 --> 00:39:47,505
I need to focus on my studies to get into college.

711
00:39:48,505 --> 00:39:50,975
I need to keep getting the scholarship too.

712
00:39:51,875 --> 00:39:53,145
I must maintain my GPA.

713
00:39:53,475 --> 00:39:54,545
My gosh.

714
00:39:55,075 --> 00:39:56,814
- Hey, have you gone mad? - How admirable.

715
00:39:56,815 --> 00:39:58,915
You really are a dutiful son.

716
00:39:58,985 --> 00:40:01,455
I bet you could even win "Show Me the Money."

717
00:40:02,025 --> 00:40:03,955
Gosh, good for Jeong Suk.

718
00:40:04,255 --> 00:40:05,255
Hey, give it back.

719
00:40:05,256 --> 00:40:08,024
Let me redo the letter with the gold dragon diamond version.

720
00:40:08,025 --> 00:40:09,025
Okay?

721
00:40:09,995 --> 00:40:10,995
Hey.

722
00:40:13,295 --> 00:40:14,465
My arm. Gosh.

723
00:40:15,905 --> 00:40:18,735
Kim Ram Woo! My gosh. Come on.

724
00:40:19,535 --> 00:40:21,275
Oh, no. Where am I?

725
00:40:21,575 --> 00:40:23,905
Hold on. Could you stop this?

726
00:40:24,275 --> 00:40:25,845
Please stop it!

727
00:40:36,025 --> 00:40:38,525
My gosh. Oh, my. Thank you.

728
00:40:44,195 --> 00:40:45,565
My gosh.

729
00:40:49,865 --> 00:40:50,935
My goodness.

730
00:40:51,835 --> 00:40:53,035
I can't believe I did that.

731
00:40:58,475 --> 00:41:00,775
