732
00:41:06,085 --> 00:41:07,115
Kim Ram Woo?

733
00:41:07,685 --> 00:41:08,685
Kim Ram Woo.

734
00:41:11,685 --> 00:41:12,755
Kim Ram Woo.

735
00:41:13,925 --> 00:41:14,995
Kim Ram Woo.

736
00:41:17,465 --> 00:41:18,495
Kim Ram Woo.

737
00:41:21,835 --> 00:41:22,865
Kim Ram Woo.

738
00:41:23,735 --> 00:41:24,735
Hey.

739
00:41:25,375 --> 00:41:26,405
Kim Ram Woo!

740
00:41:28,845 --> 00:41:29,875
Kim Ram Woo.

741
00:41:30,575 --> 00:41:31,644
Kim Ram Woo.

742
00:41:31,645 --> 00:41:34,315
Darn it. Kim Ram Woo, where are you?

743
00:41:35,015 --> 00:41:36,115
Where did he go?

744
00:41:37,415 --> 00:41:38,445
- Kim Ram Woo. - What?

745
00:41:40,215 --> 00:41:41,385
I'm right here.

746
00:41:44,155 --> 00:41:45,185
Hey.

747
00:41:45,425 --> 00:41:46,755
