750
00:41:54,165 --> 00:41:55,434
So how was it?

751
00:41:55,435 --> 00:41:57,034
Once you were up in the air, it wasn't scary at all, right?

752
00:41:57,035 --> 00:41:58,104
Wasn't it fun?

753
00:41:58,105 --> 00:41:59,205
You don't regret it, do you?

754
00:42:00,735 --> 00:42:02,205
It wasn't fun at all.

755
00:42:08,415 --> 00:42:09,845
What are you doing to celebrate your 100th day together?

756
00:42:10,615 --> 00:42:13,184
Nothing special. We'll go for a walk along the Han River.

757
00:42:13,185 --> 00:42:15,384
